title: Henry Gao’s Resume
text:
Economics and Data Science student at BYUI

My linkedin profile



Studying at BYUI as full time student, actively looking for internships related to economics, finance or data science


Statistics, Data Science, Economics, Finance, Investment, AI Algorithms



AI algorithm, automatic trading algorithm, quantitative trading.




2020-2023 Communication University of Zhejiang

GPA:3.7/4.0.
Majoring in Software Engineering

2023 - 2023 University of California Santa Barbara

GPA:3.67/4.0.
Majoring in Software Engineering

2023 - now Brigham Young University - Idaho

GPA:4.0/4.0.
Majoring in Economics and minoring in Data Science




SQL:Compiled a simulated stock trading website, deploy mysql database storage stock data and can complete various functions such as storage, calling, querying, updating data.
Python: Feed a large number of credit data samples to the deep neural network for training, and then use the trained model to test the test set, and calculate whether the customer should be given a loan based on the customer’s credit data.
Excel: Can skillfully operate excel tables to calculate the consumer index and inflation rate of local residents, and generate charts based on the data.
MS Suite: As a college student who has many years of experience, familiar with MS Suite and has used PPT in American middle school to perform cultural display.



April 2024 - Present Microeconomic Teaching Assistant

Assist professors weekly in producing teaching PPTs and provide suggestions and technical support.
Meet with students weekly in office hours to answer questions about grades and microeconomic concepts. Improve 80 students’ learning performance by giving easy-to-understand explanations and providing study suggestions
Solve 80 students’ problems related to exams, assignments and quizzes at any time according to the professor’s requirements
Help professors analyze and identify student problems and change course structures and settings to improve teaching quality
